                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable T</hi> 72.) I went to the public-house and found this hat and handkerchief with the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. We were all tipsy together—our hats fell off, and I took this hat in room of my own. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I asked him where his hat was—lit said in the stable, if I called the ostler he would produce it—I called the ostler, and then I looked round and saw this hat and handkerchief by the prosecutor's head—the next morning, as he was going to the station house, he said it was a bad job that he took it.</p>
